    "Tap **⌃Space** to open the chord HUD, then press a bound key to launch its app. ESC or any unbound key cancels. Plain Space is never observed by CapyBuddy in this mode - works correctly in password fields. (Accessibility is requested the first time you trigger a chord.)": {},
    "Tap **⌥Space** to open the chord HUD, then press a bound key to launch its app. ESC or any unbound key cancels. Plain Space is never observed by CapyBuddy in this mode - works correctly in password fields. (Accessibility is requested the first time you trigger a chord.)": {},
    "Tap **Space** for a normal space. Hold ~200ms and the chord HUD appears - then press a bound key to launch its app. (Note: macOS blocks this trigger in password fields.)": {},
